description:
Kusakari Miza is an Executive member of http://anidb.net/ch70052 [Aogiri] and the leader of the Blades, a gang in control of the 18th Ward. She comes from a clan of inbred Bikaku ghouls that hid underground. Their history of incest has resulted in poor health and dwarfism being common.
Source: Wikipedia
name: Kusakari Miza
